  "texts": [
    "We train the models on commodity hardware equipped with a 13th Gen Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-13700KF CPU at 3.40 GHz, 64 GB installed RAM and NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4090 GPU with 24 GB onboard RAM.",
    "The final model consumed 100 GPU hours during training and 10 GPU hours for evaluation.",
    "Carbon footprint.",
    "Given we train two models and an average consumption of 400 Wh we estimate the total power consumption to be 88 kWh with a carbon dioxide equivalent (CO 2e) emissions of 0.081 tonnes foot_7.",
    "To obtain a realistic measure of emissions we also need to consider multiple training experiments with different settings leading to the final models including with different hyper-parameters, prompt templates and other mix of datasets."
